title: You Are Not in Control of Other Peoples' Experiences
itunes:title: You Are Not in Control of Other Peoples' Experiences
description:
How someone reacts to you has nothing to do with you. This does not mean that you can walk around trying to piss people off and blame it on them, it means that as long as you’re living a life that is true to yourself, how other people respond to you should not be of any of your concern. We’re going to dive deep into this subject today!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
